&lt;p&gt;When you are in a deep sleep  &lt;br&gt;
There is no dream, no awareness  &lt;br&gt;
of the inside, the mind, and body  &lt;br&gt;
And no awareness of the outside world,  &lt;br&gt;
the clothes you are wearing,  &lt;br&gt;
the bed and place of your sleeping,  &lt;br&gt;
the time of your sleep,  &lt;br&gt;
persons, relatives friends, foes around you.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
